{"tid":2416320,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GIDLE梅小惠 被指涉嫌學暴事件\"打架騙錢\"……所屬公司:\"正在瞭解事實關係\"","createTime":"2021-02-21T03:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T10:42:48.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f54b0effe554f3921d6c976dfd92cfbdaeef3b48","tid":2416320,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"【dailian】gidle組合徐穗珍 被指涉嫌學暴事件&quot;打架騙錢&quot;&hellip;&hellip;所屬公司:&quot;正在瞭解事實關係&quot;<br />\n<br />\nGI-DLE成員徐穗珍捲入&quot;校園暴力&quot;風波後，經紀公司出面確認事實。<br />\n<br />\n19日，主張自己的妹妹是穗珍中學同學的A某在有關學校暴力的帖子中留言稱&quot;GI-DLE成員徐穗珍的'學暴'終於要爆發了&quot;，&quot;全世界的人都應該知道&quot;。接著，他補充道&quot;雖然我對於除一名加害者之外的其他成員感到很抱歉，但我不能再裝作不知道了&quot;。 A某還認證了穗珍上過的初中畢業照。網民們要求更多詳細說明有關穗珍學暴事件的內幕時，A某表示:&quot;這不是誤會，我是目擊者也是證人&quot;，&quot;因為不知道穗珍做了什麼的人們的玩笑，憤怒無法消除&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n​A某說:&quot;在衛生間叫我的妹妹和妹妹朋友們一起互相打對方的臉&quot;，&quot;現在節目中形象太惡心了&quot;。他還說:&quot;我妹妹每天不管在哪裡，只要一聽到GI-DLE歌曲，就會感到很累。 因為這不是虛假事實，所以即使起訴也沒有什麼不如意。&quot;與此同時，A某20日在自己的InstagramStory中上傳了疑似妹妹的人轉達的與穗珍學校暴力加害相關的內容。 根據他們的主張，穗珍平時搶別人的校服，騙取錢財。另外，還帶他們到商店的衛生間，讓他們互相打對方的臉，搶走朋友們的東西，並辱罵對方。 他還稱，穗珍與騎摩托車的人一起到處走動，飲酒和吸煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，GI-DLE的經紀公司CUBE娛樂相關人士表示:&quot;已經知道相關爭議，正在瞭解事實關係&quot;，&quot;不管怎麼說，還是等當事人發表文章後，再觀察事態發展&quot;。"},{"pid":"718a835fcafaa876a01bcc0b8d44a9a363618256","tid":2416320,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"767ef5220827927af108199f18962666064e709b","tid":2416320,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"518bcfc4eb66cea65ca212371b63b47249e316d7","tid":2416320,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74b15303e7e55c644e8562729f2f2116299d2fb8","tid":2416320,"uid":208486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:14:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afb2276a1ab77a0f5970ea08ca6a72813d7bb0ef","tid":2416320,"uid":294121,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"個樣都似啦<br />\n仲咁多紋身<br />\n一定係死太妹"},{"pid":"974b81a4e78ed6cd09a333dcd981b9c7d596b41c","tid":2416320,"uid":149494,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"佢同個Irene一樣<br />\n一睇個樣就知佢閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n韓妹d格真係無得呃"},{"pid":"128ab90ee7a987b4e9b017efe37abafd5c81804a","tid":2416320,"uid":316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"個樣都似會hey0人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed246753a1042fc5ffff7987b736985fd6ad3b00","tid":2416320,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"128ab90ee7a987b4e9b017efe37abafd5c81804a","tid":2416320,"uid":316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"個樣都似會hey0人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"舒華似D"},{"pid":"d3bed06a7d01d007b2f937bfb071c14a1dcedc85","tid":2416320,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"一睇佢個樣就知唔係好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e282738727c014a687f0651a0370ae85e717d01","tid":2416320,"uid":63198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"嘩, 仲壞過凱婷, 正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3748f6df0cc5929a4bbaec5deb71a2ee507c6258","tid":2416320,"uid":2781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:33:29.000Z","msg":"佢個樣真係唔似好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/